articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents:
About Me
My name is Matthew Ru, I am a rising sophomore at Naperville North High School in Naperville, Illinois. I like playing tennis, hanging out with my friends, gaming, and biking.
About The Project
The project titled Fuel Efficiency and Weight demonstrates the correlation between the fuel efficiency and the weight of a car.
Goals
Demonstrate the relationship between weight and fuel efficiency
Apply a similar analysis to other vehicles.
New data for such a task might be difficult to obtain

“This is Data Science”
Preceptor

Kane’s Free High School Data Science Bootcamp
